<li>Your father/husband/etc. was a remarkable man, and we will always remember his [positive quality].</li>
<li>Sending our heartfelt condolences during this incredibly challenging time.</li>
<li>We are so sorry for your loss.  May fond memories bring you comfort.</li>
<li>[Boss's name] will be dearly missed.  He/She touched so many lives.</li>
<li>Our thoughts and prayers are with you and your family.</li>
<li>Please accept our deepest sympathy. We're here for you if you need anything.</li>
<li>May peace find you in this difficult time.</li>
<li> We share in your grief and extend our deepest sympathy.</li>
<li> Thinking of you during this time of sorrow.  [Boss's name]'s memory will live on.</li>
